| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 2 | Compound allocation chains (double-alloc slice+TrimEnd, Split+LINQ+Join) |
| 🟡 Moderate | 2 | Unsealed classes (3), List\<char\>[] linear-scan symbol lookup |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

